%20to%20USASpending.gov%20contract%20data.%20Cerberus%20also%20has%20a%20large%20stake%20in%20Navistar%20Defense%2C%20a%20specialized%20military%20vehicle%20manufacturer.%20In%202021%2C%20Navistar%20paid%20a%20%2450%20million%20fine%20to%20resolve%20a%20complaint%20that%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20inflating%20the%20prices%20of%20mine-resistant%20vehicles%20it%20sold%20to%20the%20US%20Marine%20Corps%20from%202007%20to%202012%2C%20before%20Feinberg's%20firm%20bought%20a%2070%25%20stake%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20an%20even%20wider%20portfolio%20of%20responsibilities.%20Unlike%20Feinberg%2C%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20is%20set%20to%20remain%20outside%20the%20Trump%20administration%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%20would%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20potential%20divestment%20full-time%20administration%20officials%20may%20be%20asked%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20definitely%20has%20a%20vision%20for%20humanity%20and%20he%20views%20himself%20as%20a%20world%20historic%20figure%2C%20and%20he%20knows%20his%20wealth%20is%20necessary%20to%20fulfilling%20his%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Hauser%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Revolving%20Door%20Project%2C%20a%20public%20interest%20group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20earlier%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20am%20frightened%20by%20what%20government%20by%20people%20like%20that%20looks%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Trump's%20appointees%20who%20enter%20the%20government%20will%20have%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20criminal%20conflict%20of%20interest%20law.%20Congress%20did%20not%20apply%20that%20law%20to%20the%20president%20or%20vice%20president%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20constitutional%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECongressional%20Democrats%20have%20raised%20concern%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-china-favors-leave-him-exposed-nyt-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk's%20ties%20to%20China.%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20called%20for%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Rep.%20Rosa%20DeLauro%2C%20the%20top%20Democrat%20on%20the%20powerful%20House%20Appropriations%20Committee%2C%20after%20she%20and%20other%20liberal%20lawmakers%20questioned%20whether%20Musk%20helped%20kill%20a%20sweeping%20government%20funding%20bill%20due%20to%20its%20inclusion%20of%20restrictions%20on%20certain%20US%20investments%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-elon-musk-doge-conflicts-of-interest-spacex-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETime%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he's%20seen%20Musk%20put%20the%20country%20ahead%20of%20his%20financial%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20people%20that%20would%20have%20the%20credibility%20to%20do%20it%2C%20but%20he%20puts%20the%20country%20before%2C%20and%20I've%20seen%20it%2C%20before%20he%20puts%20his%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20about%20potential%20conflicts%20of%20interest%2C%20Brian%20Hughes%2C%20a%20Trump-Vance%20Transition%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20%26quot%3BAll%20nominees%20and%20appointees%20will%20comply%20with%20the%20ethical%20obligations%20of%20their%20respective%20agencies%20and%20offices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDivestment%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20navigate.%20In%202017%2C%20Florida%20Panthers%20owner%20Vincent%20Viola%2C%20a%20billionaire%2C%20withdrew%20from%20consideration%20to%20become%20Trump's%20first%20Army%20secretary.%20According%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Viola%20had%20too%20much%20difficulty%20untangling%20his%20financial%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20broker%20deals%20allowing%20them%20to%20cash%20out%20early.%20Former%20Exxon%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frex-tillerson-trump-secretary-of-state-job-2017-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERex%20Tillerson%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20work%20out%20a%20special%20%24180%20million%20retirement%20package%20with%20the%20oil%20giant%20because%20some%20of%20his%20holdings%20included%20restricted%20shares%20that%20hadn't%20been%20fully%20vested.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20accelerated%20its%20payout%20to%20Gary%20Cohn%2C%20who%20left%20the%20firm%20to%20become%20Trump's%20chief%20economic%20advisor%2C%20leaving%20him%20with%20a%20roughly%20%24285%20million%20exit%20package.%20In%20order%20to%20entice%20talent%20out%20of%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20the%20government%20also%20allows%20officials%20to%20defer%20some%20tax%20liabilities%20when%20they%20are%20directed%20to%20sell%20shares%20or%20other%20assets.%20Tillerson%20and%20Cohn%20both%20used%20this%20perk.%20So%20too%20has%20current%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Janet%20Yellen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rex%20tillerson%20donald%20trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58dae40bdd0895c67f8b4703%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20smiles%20at%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Rex%20Tillerson%20after%20he%20was%20sworn%20in%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20of%20the%20White%20House%20in%20Washington%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20Feb.%201%2C%202017.%3Cp%3EAssociated%20Perss%2FCarolyn%20Kaster%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGovernment%20watchdogs%20have%20long%20expressed%20unease%20about%20top%20officials%20entering%20the%20government%20with%20private-sector%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20advisors'%20ties%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackrocks-next-big-bet-private-markets-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlackRock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20asset%20manager%2C%20were%20the%20subject%20of%20significant%20attention%20during%20the%202020%20transition.%20Deputy%20Treasury%20Secretary%20Wally%20Adeyemo%20was