n%20for%20defeating%20zombies.%20Here%2C%20a%20participant%20readied%20for%20a%20Zombie%20Survival%20contest%20in%20Spain%20in%202022.%3Cp%3EPablo%20Blazquez%20Dominguez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20military's%20war%20plan%20for%20fighting%20zombies%20began%20from%20a%20training%20scenario.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20focuses%20on%20identifying%20the%20enemy%2C%20designating%20vital%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20coordinating%20forces.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20military%20has%20real-world%20experience%20in%20responding%20to%20disasters%20and%20outbreaks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20zombies%20attack%2C%20the%20US%20military%20has%20a%20plan.%20Really.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20authorization%20from%20the%20president%20or%20the%20defense%20secretary%2C%20US%20Strategic%20Command%20will%20begin%20preparations%20for%20safeguarding%20the%20civilian%20population%2C%20protecting%20vital%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20eradicating%20the%20zombie%20menace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20all%20without%20violating%20the%20rights%20of%20threatened%20humans%20and%20possibly%20the%20zombies%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20plan%20was%20not%20actually%20designed%20as%20a%20joke%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocuments.theblackvault.com%2Fdocuments%2Fcontroversies%2FCONPLAN8888-11.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECONPLAN%208888-11%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%26quot%3BCounter%20Zombie%20Dominance%26quot%3B)%2C%20issued%20on%20April%2030%2C%202011%20by%20USSTRATCOM%2C%20whose%20normal%20responsibilities%20include%20overseeing%20America's%20strategic%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20global%20strike%20capabilities%20and%20missile%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20originated%20as%20a%20scenario%20to%20train%20junior%20officers%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20Joint%20Operation%20Planning%20and%20Execution%20System%20(JOPES)%2C%20by%20which%20the%20US%20military%20devises%20contingency%20plans.%20Instructors%20discovered%20that%20a%20zombie%20apocalypse%20scenario%20was%20a%20better%20teaching%20tool%20than%20using%20fictional%20scenarios%20about%20Tunisia%20or%20Nigeria%20as%20was%20customary%20at%20the%20time%2C%20which%20also%20risked%20being%20misunderstood%20by%20the%20public%20as%20real%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20elected%20to%20use%20a%20completely%20impossible%20scenario%20that%20could%20never%20be%20mistaken%20as%20a%20real%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20the%20CONPLAN%208888-11%20document.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20plan%20was%20so%20ridiculous%2C%20our%20students%20not%20only%20enjoyed%20the%20lessons%3B%20they%20actually%20were%20able%20to%20explore%20the%20basic%20concepts%20of%20plan%20and%20order%20development%20(fact%2C%20assumptions%2C%20specified%20and%20implied%20tasks%2C%20references%20etc.)%20very%20effectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20tongue%20in%20cheek%20%E2%80%94%20or%20shot%20to%20the%20head%20%E2%80%94%20the%20plan%20lays%20out%20how%20USSTRATCOM%20will%20handle%20a%20global%20uprising%20of%20the%20undead.%20When%20the%20US%20military%20goes%20on%20Zombie%20Condition%20(ZombieCon)%20alert%2C%20Strategic%20Command%20will%20begin%20defensive%20operations%20to%20protect%20the%20human%20population%2C%20and%20offensive%20operations%20to%20neutralize%20zombies%20by%20%26quot%3Bdenial%2C%20deception%2C%20disruption%2C%20degradation%20or%20destruction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20looking%20for%20tactical%20tips%20on%20killing%20flesh-eating%20monsters%20will%20be%20disappointed.%20CONPLAN%208888-11%20is%20a%20staff%20plan%20that%20focuses%20on%20identifying%20the%20enemy%2C%20designating%20vital%20infrastructure%20such%20as%20food%2C%20power%20and%20medical%20care%2C%20and%20coordinating%20friendly%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20full%20advantage%20of%20abundant%20open-source%20intelligence%20on%20the%20undead%2C%20planners%20mined%20classic%20movies%20and%20popular%20video%20games%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BWorld%20War%20Z%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BNight%20of%20the%20Living%20Dead%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPlants%20vs%20Zombies%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20devise%20a%20typology%20of%20zombies.%20These%20include%20those%20infected%20by%20a%20virus%20or%20mutated%20by%20radiation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20caused%20by%20magic%2C%20extraterrestrials%2C%20and%20human%20engineering%20(%26quot%3BWeaponized%20Zombies%26quot%3B).%20There%20are%20also%20vegetarian%20zombies%2C%20which%20consume%20grain%20and%20thus%20threaten%20the%20US%20food%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20predator%2C%20zombies%20will%20go%20where%20their%20prey%20can%20be%20found.%20Undead%20armies%20are%20expected%20to%20focus%20on%20cities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20water%20sources%20(humans%20need%20water%2C%20but%20zombies%20don't).%20While%20zombies%20don't%20drive%20vehicles%2C%20preferring%20walking%20or%20running%20with%20outstretched%20arms%2C%20roads%20will%20be%20crucial%20transportation%20arteries%20for%20human%20soldiers%20as%20well%20as%20crowds%20of%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECONPLAN%208888-11%20is%20a%20multiphase%20plan%20to%20put%20down%20a%20zombie%20outbreak.%20Preparations%20will%20begin%20prewar%20with%20USSTRATCOM%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%20surveillance%20to%20detect%20%26quot%3Bdisease%20vectors%20that%20could%20cause%20zombieism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20will%20also%20try%20to%20deter%20anyone%20from%20creating%20zombies.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20zombies%20are%20not%20cognizant%20life-forms%2C%26quot%3B%20USSTRATCOM%20pointed%20out.%20%26quot%3BAs%20such%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3Edeterred%20or%20reasoned%20with%20in%20any%20way.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20zombie-inducing%20forces%20that%20can%20be%20deterred%20from%20further%20action.%20These%20forces%20include%20but%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20nation%20states%20and%20terrorist%20groups%20with%20%5Bweapons%20of%20mass%20destruction%5D%20programs%2C%20and%20unethical%20bio-research%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20outbreak%20begins%2C%20American%20forces%20will%20mobilize%2C%20though%20CONPLAN%208888-11%20cautions%20that%20to%20avoid%20rattling%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20there%20must%20be%20%26quot%3Bconfidence-building%20measures%20to%20ensure%20leaders%20within%20these%20nations%20do%20not%20construe%20USSTRATCOM%20preparations%20to%20counter%20zombie-dominance%20as%20preparations%20for%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%2040%20days%20after%20the%20outbreak%2C%20the%20US%20military%20will%20on%20the%20offensive.%20Once%20the%20zombies%20have%20been%20wiped%2C%20USSTRATCOM%20will%20assess%20the%20damage%20and%20begin%20reestablishing%20civil%20authority.%20Though%20some%20other%20organization%20will%20have%20to%20provide%20the%20zombie-busting%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20hold%20off%20the%20Zombie%20horde%20far%20so%20the%20military%20can%20strike%20it%20with%20overwhelming%20firepower.%20%26quot%3BUSSTRATCOM%20has%20no%20ground%20combat%20forces%20capable%20of%20repelling%20a%20zombie%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20CONPLAN%208888-11%20notes.%20%26quot%3BUSSTRATCOM%20can%20only%20deliver%20synchronized%20fires%20against%20a%20zombie%20threat%20via%20strategic%20air%2C%20space%20and%20maritime%20forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20include%20nuclear%20weapons.%20USSTRATCOM%20must%20%26quot%3Bmaintain%20emergency%20plans%20to%20employ%20nuclear%20weapons%20within%20CONUS%20%5Bcontinental%20United%20States%5D%20to%20eradicate%20zombie%20hordes%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20potential%20hurdle%20to%20deploying%20the%20US%20military%20is%20lawfare.%20Laws%20such%20as%20the%20Insurrection%20and%20the%20Posse%20Comitatus%20Acts%20strictly%20limit%20the%20deployment%20of%20the%20US%20military%20in%20domestic%20affairs.%20Though%20martial%20law%20would%20almost%20certainly%20be%20declared%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20mass%20zombie%20plague%2C%20deployment%20against%20undead%20who%20were%20formerly%20living%20US%20citizens%20could%20raise%20questions%20of%20Constitutional%20rights%2C%20as%20well%20as%20various%20international%20treaties%20and%20UN%20charters%20governing%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20conduct%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%20whether%20zombies%20are%20still%20US%20citizens%20or%20pathogens%20who%20can%20be%20killed.%20%26quot%3BUS%20and%20international%20law%20regulate%20military%20operations%20only%20insofar%20as%20human%20and%20animal%20life%20are%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20CONPLAN%208888-11%20argued.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20almost%20no%20restrictions%20on%20hostile%20actions%20that%20may%20be%20taken%20either%20defensively%20or%20offensively%20against%20pathogenic%20life%20forms%2C%20organic-robotic%20entities%2C%20or%20'traditional'%20zombies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20meant%20as%20a%20fun%20training%20exercise%2C%20would%20USSTRATCOM's%20plan%20actually%20work%3F%20The%20US%20military%20obviously%20lacks%20experience%20in%20counter-zombie%20operations%20but%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20infectious%20disease%20response%20like%20the%202014%20Ebola%20outbreak%20in%20West%20Africa.%20It%20has%20also%20gained%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20in%20responding%20to%20natural%20catastrophes%20and%20manmade%20disasters%2C%20as%20well%20as%20reestablishing%20civil%20authority%20in%20devastated%20places%20such%20as%20post-World%20War%20II%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFictional%20movies%20and%20books%20about%20zombies%20abound.%20We%20can%20only%20hope%20this%20is%20one%20real-life%20contingency%20plan%20that%20never%20gets%20dusted%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%