0I%20would%20say%2C%20mid-senior%20level%20or%20something%20around%20director%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20doing%20this%20work%20for%20more%20than%2010%20years%2C%20quite%20successfully%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20toot%20my%20own%20horn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20recruiter%20told%20me%20I%20was%20super%20qualified%20but%20said%20I%20was%20probably%20hitting%20bumps%20because%20when%20you%20get%20to%20my%20level%20of%20experience%2C%20many%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20manage%20teams.%20Then%2C%20the%20recruiter%20told%20me%20I%20might%20have%20to%20consider%20looking%20for%20a%20more%20junior%20role%20because%20most%20managing%20jobs%20would%20be%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20conversation%20now%20about%20remote%20work%20goes%20beyond%20it%20just%20being%20a%20perk.%20It's%20almost%20like%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ceo-eric-schmidt-criticism-remote-work-google-openai-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20drawback%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20some%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20condition%20requiring%20the%20nurse%20three%20times%20a%20day%20is%20the%20reason%20that%20remote%20has%20gone%20from%20a%20luxury%20for%20me%20to%20now%20being%20a%20necessity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20my%20insurance%20works%2C%20it%20only%20allows%20the%20nurse%20to%20come%20to%20one%20address.%20So%2C%20even%20if%20I%20were%20to%20find%20a%20job%20here%20in%20South%20Florida%2C%20I%20would%20still%20have%20to%20be%20remote%20because%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218f9020e-edca-4eea-9320-21b218e04a3c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20this%20care%20took%20decades%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%2020%20years%20on%20a%20waiting%20list%20to%20get%20this%20level%20of%20home%20care%20by%20a%20nurse%20covered%20through%20Medicaid.%20If%20I%20leave%20Florida%20and%20go%20anywhere%20else%2C%20I%20lose%20those%20services%20and%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%