0started%20trying%20to%20run%20to%20my%20grandma's%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2027-year-old%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%202-mile%20run%20through%20Chicago%20was%20a%20challenge.%20But%20gradually%20Ollearis%20built%20up%20to%20a%20half-marathon.%20After%20completing%20the%20half%2C%20she%20challenged%20herself%20to%20run%20a%20full%20marathon%20on%20her%2023rd%20birthday%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ambitious%20goal%20gave%20her%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%2C%20something%20to%20work%20toward.%20Since%20official%20races%20were%20still%20canceled%2C%20she%20completed%20the%2026.2%20miles%20on%20her%20own.%20%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20parked%20up%20in%20the%20park%20and%20just%20hung%20out%20all%20day%2C%20and%20I%20just%20ran%20circles%20around%20the%20park%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20cyclist%20in%20college%2C%20Ollearis%20was%20used%20to%20training%20for%20a%20race%20%E2%80%94%20the%20clear%20objective%20helped%20her%20stay%20focused%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-americans-dont-exercise-mental-health-crisis-depression-anxiety-fitness-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emotivated%20to%20work%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20also%20realized%20that%20running%20was%20about%20more%20than%20the%20physical%20challenge.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20about%20discovering%20what%20I'm%20capable%20of%20and%20constantly%20pushing%20my%20limits%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Ollearis%20has%20since%20run%20two%20official%20marathons%2C%20three%20Ironmans%2C%20and%20three%20ultramarathons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20especially%20are%20taking%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20droves.%20In%20the%20most%20recent%20New%20York%20City%20Marathon%2C%20women%20between%2025%20and%2029%20outnumbered%20every%20other%20age%20and%20gender%20segment%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20reversal%20from%20the%20years%20when%20men%20in%20their%2040s%20were%20dominant.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20the%20first%20marathons%20were%20held%20in%20the%20late%2019th%20century%2C%20they%20were%20thought%20to%20be%20safe%20only%20for%20young%2C%20fit%20men%3B%20people%20thought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1996%2F06%2F23%2Fmagazine%2Fhow-the-women-won.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20would%20make%20women%20infertile%20or%20overly%20masculine%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20Gen%20Z%20women%20in%20the%20US%20are%20joining%20Strava%20twice%20as%20fast%20as%20they%20did%20in%202023%2C%20making%20them%20the%20app's%20fastest-growing%20demographic.%20Women%20%26quot%3Bare%20constantly%20being%20told%20to%20shrink%20and%20slow%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Ollearis%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20be%20that%20woman%20who%20shows%20up%20and%20is%20strong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20watching%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20couch%2C%20it%20might%20seem%20masochistic%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealth-benefits-of-running-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrain%20for%20and%20run%20a%20marathon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20let%20alone%20an%20ultramarathon.%20But%20Kevin%20Masters%2C%20a%20clinical%20psychologist%20who%20teaches%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%2C%20says%20participating%20in%20extreme%20fitness%20challenges%20can%20help%20people%20find%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose.%20It%20sets%20a%20goal%20that%20is%20attainable%20but%20not%20easy.%20For%20young%20people%20who%20graduated%20into%20an%20uncertain%20and%20shifting%20world%2C%20purpose%20was%20a%20hot%20commodity.%20In%20a%202023%20Gallup%20survey%2C%20between%2043%25%20and%2049%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20said%20they%20didn't%20feel%20like%20what%20they%20did%20each%20day%20was%20interesting%2C%20important%2C%20or%20motivating.%20%26quot%3BRunning%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20things%20people%20could%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Adharanand%20Finn%2C%20the%2050-year-old%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Rise%20of%20The%20Ultra%20Runners.%26quot%3B%20He%20noticed%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20get%20into%20running%20during%20the%20pandemic%20lockdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20without%20a%20pandemic%2C%20navigating%20your%20mid-20s%20is%20tricky.%20As%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-hustle-generation-jobs-work-side-hustle-freelance-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20goalposts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20homeownership%2C%20marriage%2C%20and%20parenthood%20get%20pushed%20further%20back%2C%20many%20young%20people%20are%20looking%20for%20other%20ways%20to%20measure%20their%20progress%20and%20regain%20a%20sense%20of%20control.%20Some%20are%20calling%20it%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Ffamily%2Farchive%2F2024%2F04%2Frunning-marathon-quarter-life-crisis%2F678156%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equarter-life%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20there's%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-become-an-influencer-instagram-tiktok-youtube-snapchat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfluencer%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20more%20people%20got%20into%20running%2C%20more%20people%20posted%20about%20it%2C%20which%20influenced%20more%20people%20to%20get%20into%20running%2C%20which%20led%20to%20more%20running%20influencers.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20running%20has%20become%20cool%3B%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWrAuX1K2eoM%26t%3D1407s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20about%20the%20running%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Keltie%20O'Connor%2C%20a%20college%20basketball%20player%20turned%20fitness%20YouTuber%2C%20said%20that%20was%20one%20reason%20more%20people%20were%20doing%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%20%E2%80%94%20companies%20caught%20on%20and%20they%20made%20things%20cool%3A%20like%20On%20Cloud%2C%20and%20then%20Oakley%20sunglasses%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BRunning%20suddenly%20got%20a%20cool%20factor%2C%20and%20brands%20jumped%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20TikTok%2C%20Instagram%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Strava%2C%20it's%20now%20easy%20to%20find%20inspiration%20to%20push%20yourself%20%E2%80%94%20a%20different%20reality%20from%20when%20Finn%20was%20running%20ultramarathons%20in%202017.%20Back%20then%2C%20he%20says%2C%20ultra%20running%20was%20a%20niche%20sport.%20Now%20budding%20racers%20can%20open%20TikTok%20and%20follow%20someone's%20training%20plan%20from%20day%20one%20to%20race%20day.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20get%20sucked%20in%2C%20you%20start%20following%20people%20on%20Instagram%2C%20meeting%20other%20runners%2C%20buying%20the%20kit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20before%20you%20know%20it%2C%20you%20are%20running%20a%20marathon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20running%20world%20has%20become%20a%20robust%20community%20for%20young%20people.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20music-festival%20vibe%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Connor%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20more%20people%20turning%20to%20sober%20living%20and%20wanting%20to%20meet%20people%20outside%20the%20club%20and%20not%20feeling%20like%20they%20have%20to%20have%20a%20drink%20just%20to%20meet%20someone%2C%20they%20can%20sign%20up%20to%20a%20race%20or%20join%20a%20run%20club%20and%20meet%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20once%20you've%20got%20a%20marathon%20under%20your%20belt%2C%20you%20can%20either%20go%20faster%20or%20farther.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20first%20marathon%2C%20Ollearis%20decided%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20an%20Ironman.%20For%20six%20months%20she%20trained%20every%20day.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20swimming%20on%20Monday%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20Friday.%20I%20was%20running%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Saturday%2C%20and%20I%20was%20biking%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Sunday%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Training%20took%20over%20her%20life%20for%20a%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20she%20often%20turned%20down%20social%20events%2C%20prioritizing%20recovery%20over%20late%20nights%20out.%20She%20has%20no%20regrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20gave%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20purpose.%20It%20gave%20me%20a%20reason%20to%20show%20up%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%20at%20times%2C%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I%20missed%20out%20%E2%80%94%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20built%20something%20I'm%20really%20proud%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOllearis%20began%20documenting%20her%20Ironman%20journey%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40ryleejade.fit%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20her%20following%20grew%20by%20100%2C000.%20The%20more%20she%20posted%2C%20the%20more%20her%20follower%20count%20grew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20became%20an%20experiment%20of%20how%20far%20can%20this%20go%20and%20can%20I%20turn%20this%20into%20something%20bigger%20than%20just%20the%20race%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20This%20year%20Ollearis%20was%20able%20to%20quit%20her%20full-time%20job%20and%20focus%20on%20online%20coaching%20and%20content%20creation.%20In%20October%20she%20ran%20the%20Chicago%20Marathon%20%E2%80%94%20which%20had%20a%20record%20number%20of%20runners%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20sponsorship%20from%20the%20brand%20Biofreeze.%20She%20hit%20a%20personal%20record.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20nowhere%20near%20the%20professional%20level%2C%20but%20I%20am%20still%20getting%20paid%20to%20work%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20It's%20the%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20part%20of%20the%20flood%20of%20new%20running%20influencers%20who%20have%20gained%20traction%20by%20posting%20about%20their%20running%20journey%20or%20training%20routines.%20To%20stand%20out%2C%20creators%20have%20to%20up%20the%20stakes.%20When%20Chase%20Bandolik%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20gym%20owner%20from%20Chicago%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20colleagues%20to%20donate%20to%20his%20first%20marathon%20in%202019%2C%20he%20told%20them%20that%20if%20he%20raised%20%241%2C800%20for%20charity%20he%20would%20run%20wearing%20a%20weighted%20vest.%20%26quot%3BI%20ended%20up%20running%20a%20marathon%20with%20a%20weighted%20vest%20before%20I%20ever%20ran%20a%20marathon%20without%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20there%20I%20got%20kind%20of%20addicted%20to%20that%20feeling%20of%20having%20a%20really%20hard%20goal%20and%20finding%20a%20way%20to%20get%20it%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20he%20ran%20his%20first%20100-mile%20ultramarathon%20%E2%80%94%20he%20ran%20on%20a%20treadmill%20for%2017%20hours%2C%20briefly%20slowing%20to%20a%20walk%20every%20five%20miles%20to%20eat%20or%20drink.%20Then%20he%20signed%20up%20for%20an%20Ironman.%20Bandolik%20enjoyed%20the%20accountability%20that%20came%20with%20posting%20his%20progress%20online.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20times%20at%20these%20races%20there%20are%20people%20who%20sign%20up%20and%20don't%20even%20show%20up%20or%20give%20up%20early%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20But%20when%20you're%20sharing%20everything%20with%20your%20followers%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20extra%20pressure%20to%20finish%20it%20and%20get%20the%20job%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBandolik's%20goal%20for%20this%20year%20is%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Backyard%20Ultra%20championships%20%E2%80%94%20a%20race%20where%20competitors%20run%20a%204-mile%20loop%20every%20hour%20until%20only%20one%20runner%20is%20left.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cool%20thing%20about%20the%20endurance%20world%20is%20there's%20so%20many%20directions%20to%20take%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20creating%20longer%20and%20longer%20and%20harder%20and%20harder%20races.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20young%20people%20who%20might%20feel%20like%20traditional%20life%20benchmarks%20are%20out%20of%20reach%2C%20competing%20means%20there's%20always%20another%20milestone%20to%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Feve-upton-clark%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3