0blowing%20up%20vehicles%2C%20artillery%2C%20and%20bunkers%20and%20clearing%20a%20path%20for%20friendly%20ground%20troops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20Ukrainian%20combat%20drone%20pilot%20who%20believes%20that%20armies%20need%20to%20create%20a%20separate%20branch%20for%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20system%20(UAS)%20and%20electromagnetic%20warfare%20%E2%80%94%20and%20go%20on%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BBreakthroughs%20with%20large%20mechanized%20formations%20are%20becoming%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%20and%20static%20warfare%2C%20like%20the%20positional%20stalemate%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20new%20norm%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Illya%20Sekirin%20in%20an%20article%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchacr.org.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FBAR-190.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBritish%20Army%20Review%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20UAS%20and%20electromagnetic%20warfare%20branch%20would%20be%20particularly%20useful%20in%20breaching%20enemy%20fortified%20positions%20through%20the%20use%20of%20massed%20offensive%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDrones%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20artillery%20%E2%80%94%20have%20become%20the%20dominant%20weapons%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20In%20particular%2C%20while%20tanks%20are%20still%20a%20major%20weapon%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20they%20no%20longer%20enjoy%20the%20dominance%20they%20once%20had.%20Hordes%20of%20small%20first-person-view%20(FPV)%20drones%20have%20made%20life%20hazardous%20for%20hulking%2C%20expensive%20weapons%20such%20as%20armored%20vehicles%20and%20artillery%20pieces%2C%20which%20now%20operate%20cautiously%20and%20under%20the%20protection%20of%20air%20defense%20and%20electronic%20warfare%20systems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFPV%20drones%20(also%20known%20as%20loitering%20munitions)%20have%20become%20so%20effective%20that%20they%2C%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20around%20%24350%20to%20%24450%20per%20asset%2C%20can%20now%20be%20described%20as%20the%20Ukrainian%20army's%20principal%20anti-tank%20weapon%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Sekirin%2C%20who%20has%20combat%20experience%20operating%20the%20DJI%20Mavic%203%2C%20a%20piloted%20drone%20popular%20with%20hobbyists%20as%20well%20as%20Ukrainian%20soldiers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mines%2C%20drones%20and%20obstacles%20in%20Ukraine%20have%20hampered%20the%20power%20of%20tanks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676ddbac9de00e389eb38804%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMines%2C%20drones%20and%20obstacles%20in%20Ukraine%20have%20hampered%20the%20power%20of%20tanks.%3Cp%3EWolfgang%20Schwan%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESekirin%20wants%20to%20take%20this%20to%20the%20next%20level.%20Breaching%20fortified%20lines%2C%20as%20both%20the%20Russians%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcis.mit.edu%2Fpublications%2Fanalysis-opinion%2F2023%2Fukraine-has-breakthrough-problem%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUkrainians%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%2C%20is%20a%20complex%20and%20fraught%20operation%20that%20often%20results%20in%20heavy%20casualties%20to%20the%20assault%20troops.%20Sekirin's%20alternative%3A%20using%20immense%20numbers%20of%20drones%20to%20blast%20a%20hole%20in%20enemy%20defenses%20that%20creates%20breathing%20room%20for%20assault%20troops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%2040%2C000%20drones%20that%20would%20attack%20in%20waves%20to%20destroy%20enemy%20forces%20in%20a%20frontline%20area%2010%20kilometers%20%5B6%20miles%5D%20and%2020%20kilometers%20%5B12%20miles%5D%20deep%2C%20with%20a%20resulting%20drone%20attack%20density%20of%20200%20UASs%20per%20square%20kilometer%2C%26quot%3B%20Sekirin%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThis%20drone%20attack%20would%20simultaneously%20provide%20accurate%20covering%20fire%20to%20friendly%20mine-clearing%20vehicles%20and%20advancing%20mechanized%20infantry%20units%20tasked%20with%20capturing%20the%20area.%20Through%20the%20resulting%20breach%20of%20the%20frontline%2C%20conventional%20maneuver%20forces%20could%20then%20enter%20to%20gain%20the%20operational%20initiative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESekirin%20argues%20that%20using%20drones%20for%20breaching%20operations%20saves%20money%20and%20reduces%20friendly%20casualties.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20price%20of%20an%20average%20attack%20drone%20is%20presumed%20to%20be%20%24500%2C%20drones%20would%20cost%20%2420%20million%2C%20which%20is%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20the%20price%20of%20just%20two%20Ml%20Abrams%20tanks.%2040%2C000%20UASs%20would%20also%20constitute%20only%200.8%20percent%20of%20worldwide%20consumer%20drone%20shipments%20(five%20million%20units%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F1234658%2Fworldwide-consumer-drone-unit-shipments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshipped%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202020)%2C%20suggesting%20that%20production%20and%20supply%20issues%20would%20not%20be%20an%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20goes%20well%20beyond%20drone%20use%20in%20the%20nearly%20three-year%20war%2C%20which%20has%20mostly%20been%20to%20try%20to%20disable%20vehicles%20and%20to%20stalk%20small%20groups%20of%20soldiers.%20Making%20drones%20into%20a%20massive%20strike%20force%20would%20require%20enhanced%20communication%20and%20tactics%20to%20limit%20friendly%20fire%20on%20advancing%20troops%2C%20who%20can%20resemble%20those%20of%20their%20enemy%20on%20grainy%20video%20or%20infrared%20feeds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20ironic%20is%20that%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20tanks%20were%20invented%20precisely%20as%20a%20means%20to%20breach%20the%20fortified%20trench%20lines%20of%20the%20First%20World%20War%20that%20had%20largely%20been%20closely%20defended%20by%20machine%20guns.%20World%20War%20II%20saw%20armies%20rely%20on%20masses%20of%20tanks%20not%20just%20to%20penetrate%20defense%20lines%2C%20but%20also%20to%20use%20their%20mobility%20and%20firepower%20to%20smash%20enemy%20forces%20and%20capture%20vast%20amounts%20of%20territory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20Sekirin's%20concept%20would%20have%20drones%20assume%20the%20historical%20role%20of%20tanks.%20But%20that%20raises%20questions%20in%20itself.%20As%20soon%20as%20tanks%20made%20their%20debut%20in%201916%2C%20it%20quickly%20became%20clear%20that%20they%20were%20not%20a%20miracle%20solution%20for%20battlefield%20problems.%20Armored%20vehicles%20then%20and%20now%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20weapons%2C%20which%20means%20they%20must%20use%20combined%20arms%20tactics%20in%20which%20they%20coordinate%20with%20other%20arms%20such%20as%20infantry%2C%20artillery%2C%20engineers%20and%20aircraft.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20they%20are%20cheap%20and%20easy%20to%20manufacture%20in%20quantity%2C%20it%20would%20be%20tempting%20for%20armies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20penny-pinching%20politicians%20%E2%80%94%20to%20rely%20on%20a%20massive%20fleet%20of%20drones%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20traditional%20breaching%20systems%20such%20as%20combat%20engineers%20and%20mine-clearing%20tanks.%20But%20just%20as%20tanks%20became%20vulnerable%20to%20mines%2C%20anti-tank%20rockets%20and%20now%20drones%2C%20the%20drones%20themselves%20will%20likely%20fall%20prey%20to%20countermeasures%20such%20as%20jamming%20(which%20already%20is%20disrupting%20UAV%20operations%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20projectile%20weapons%20and%20intercept%20drones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20horde%20of%2040%2C000%20drones%20would%20be%20an%20impressive%20and%20scary%20sight.%20But%20it%20is%20no%20panacea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ETwitter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-swarm-smash-russian-defenses-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735724461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676dd89f9de00e389eb387b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-swarm-smash-russian-defenses-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Ukrainian%20drone%20flyer%20argues%20a%20massive%20swarm%20could%20clear%20a%20path%20through%20Russian%20defenses%20for%20infantry%20and%20tanks%20to%20follow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-swarm-smash-russian-defenses-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20things%20to%20do%20to%20protect%20yourself%20online%20from%20scams%20and%20hacks%20in%20the%20new%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223543%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20computer%20user%20types%20a%20password%20into%20a%20box%20on%20a%20login%20page.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67744477e5726ab18d0e31fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222362%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScammers%20and%20hackers%20have%20embraced%20AI%20to%20make%20their%20attempts%20more%20realistic.%3Cp%3EJakub%20Porzycki%2FNurPhoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcybersecurity%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHackers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20scammers%20are%20getting%20more%20sophisticated%20in%20their%20methods.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElaborate%20social%20engineering%20schemes%20and%20AI%20are%20some%20ways%20that%20scammers%20are%20upping%20their%20game.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20cybersecurity%20expert%20explained%20four%20ways%20to%20protect%20yourself%20going%20into%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20end-of-2024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-treasury-computer-hack-china-beyondtrust-cybersecurity-breach-salt-typhoon-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehack%20of%20US%20Treasury%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%20computers%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20if%20the%20government%20isn't%20immune%20to%20tech%20trouble%2C%20neither%20are%20you.%20So%2C%20keeping%20your%20online%20accounts%20and%20information%20secure%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20state-backed%20hackers%20like%20the%20ones%20suspected%20of%20tapping%20into%20the%20Treasury's%20computers%20are%20sophisticated%2C%20there%20are%20still%20threats%20from%20small-time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-cyber-crime-phishing-malware-artificial-intelligence-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybercriminals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Etay%20Maor%2C%20chief%20security%20strategist%20at%20Cato%20Networks%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20individuals%20can%20use%20various%20tactics%20to%20avoid%20hackers%20and%20scammers%20gaining%20access%20to%20their%20information.%20Many%20have%20been%20around%20for%20years%2C%20but%20recent%20developments%2C%20such%20as%20the%20rise%20of%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20call%20for%20new%20strategies%2C%20Maor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pain%20to%20remember%20another%20password%20or%20to%20enable%20another%20application%20to%20send%20you%20an%20SMS%2C%26quot%3B%20Maor%20said.%20But%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt'll%20help%20you%20not%20be%20the%20lower-hanging%20fruit%26quot%3B%20for%20those%20smaller%20hackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20four%20tips%20for%20enhancing%20cybersecurity%20and%20avoiding%20hackers%20and%20digital%20scammers%20going%20into%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22378d7b50-846d-40f6-85ad-6bfeb94ac1d4%5C%22%3EUse%20strong%20passwords%20%E2%80%94%20and%20have%20a%20secure%20place%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20same%20password%20repeatedly%20for%20different%20accounts%20makes%20a%20scammer's%20job%20easier%2C%20Maor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20some%20long-standing%20advice%3A%20Create%20a%20separate%20password%20for%20each%20account%2C%20and%20make%20each%20one%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20usually%2C%20at%20least%20several%20characters%20long%2C%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20letters%2C%20numbers%2C%20and%20punctuation%20marks%2C%20and%20without%20common%20words%20or%20sequences%20like%20%26quot%3B123456%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20keeping%20track%20of%20all%20those%20passwords%20can%20be%20tough.%20Maor%20said%20he%20has%20a%20pattern%20that%20he%20uses%20to%20create%20new%20passwords.%20It's%20mostly%20secure%2C%20though%20he%20said%20that%20hackers%20might%20be%20able%20to%20figure%20out%20his%20pattern%20if%20they%20got%20enough%20of%20his%20passwords.%20There%20is%20also%20password-keeping%20software%2C%20but%20bad%20actors%20can%20hack%20those%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20a%20more%20secure%20option%20is%20a%20low-tech%20one%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20writing%20them%20down%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20is%20much%20more%20secure%20than%20having%20the%20same%20password%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Maor%20said.%20Just%20make%20sure%20you%20don't%20leave%20it%20lying%20around%20in%20plain%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269114896-38c4-4eaf-99a4-55863bcf3bde%5C%22%3EBe%20aware%20of%20social%20engineering%20scams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20scammers%20don't%20use%20AI%20but%20instead%20rely%20on%20their%20own%20communication%20and%20relationship-building%20skills%20to%20steal%20money%20or%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBasic%20versions%20of%20this%20scam%20can%20include%20direct%20messages%20from%20people%20on%20Facebook%20or%20other%20social%20media%20apps%20who%20try%20to%20befriend%20you%20before%20asking%20for%20money%20or%20personal%20information%2C%20Maor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20are%20more%20sophisticated%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20now%20an%20attacker%20and%20I%20want%20to%20attack%20your%20boss%2C%20I%20might%20connect%20with%20you%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20then%20I'll%20try%20to%20connect%20with%20your%20boss%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20That%20will%20create%20a%20mutual%20connection%20that%20could%20make%20the%20hacker%20appear%20more%20credible%20to%20the%20boss%2C%20Maor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210867fc2-c867-45c9-af84-745b4c2991fe%5C%22%3EAvoid%20AI-based%20scams%20by%20making%20a%20plan%20with%20family%20and%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20scammers%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-voice-generator-phone-scam-imposter-crime-money-cash-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20voice%20generators%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20create%20convincing%20clips%20of%20people%20saying%20they're%20in%20trouble%20and%20need%20money.%20The%20scammers%20then%20call%20the%20subject's%20friends%20and%20relatives%20and%20use%20the%20AI-generated%20voice%20to%20rip%20them%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaor%20said%20he%20already%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20avoid%20such%20scams%20with%20his%20family%3A%20They%20have%20agreed%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecret%20word%26quot%3B%20they%20can%20ask%20for%20if%20they%20get%20a%20request%20they%20suspect%20might%20be%20AI-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20something%20very%20common%2C%26quot%3B%20Maor%20said%20of%20the%20word%20his%20family%20picked.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20we%20shouldn't%20be%20afraid%20to%20do%20that%20in%20our%20corporate%20environment%20and%20in%20a%20private%20environment%20as%20well%2C%20just%20to%20confirm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20also%20made%20phishing%20scams%2C%20which%20typically%20involve%20scammers%20sending%20emails%20that%20look%20like%20they're%20from%20a%20reputable%20source%20in%20order%20to%20get%20personal%20information%20about%20the%20recipient%2C%20more%20convincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20guidance%20for%20avoiding%20phishing%20scams%20suggests%20looking%20for%20obvious%20typos%20in%20emails%20to%20identify%20potential%20phishing%20scams%2C%20Maor%20said.%20But%20scammers%20can%20now%20use%20AI%20to%20create%20grammatically%20passable%20messages%20in%20any%20language%20they%20need%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226898eb8c-3dea-4577-afe5-2bd224d4b5aa%5C%22%3EMake%20sure%20to%20use%20two-factor%20authentication%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20been%20around%20for%20years%2C%20two-factor%20authentication%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%2C%20asking%20a%20website%20or%20app%20to%20send%20you%20a%20code%20via%20email%2C%20text%2C%20or%20call%20that%20you%20must%20enter%20in%20addition%20to%20your%20password%20to%20log%20in%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20a%20good%20way%20to%20protect%20unauthorized%20people%20from%20accessing%20your%20accounts%2C%20Maor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20possible%20to%20use%20an%20authenticator%20app%20like%20Duo%20or%20Microsoft%20Authenticator%20to%20sign%20off%20on%20login%20attempts%20or%20a%20physical%20security%20key%2C%20which%2C%20when%20used%20near%20the%20computer%2C%20confirms%20that%20it's%20really%20you%20trying%20to%20log%20in%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconsumer.ftc.gov%2Farticles%2Fprotect-your-personal-information-hackers-and-scammers%23accounts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Trade%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-protect-yourself-from-hacks-or-scams-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735724281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677444b39de00e389eb405bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-protect-yourself-from-hacks-or-scams-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hackers%20and%20scammers%20are%20using%20AI%2C%20social%20engineering%2C%20and%20other%20methods%20to%20gain%20personal%20information.%20Here's%20how%20to%20shield%20yourself.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-protect-yourself-from-hacks-or-scams-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AAP%20vs%20BJP%20Letter%20War%20On%20New%20Year's%20Day%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Writes%20To%20RSS%20Head%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20campaign%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Election%2C%20party%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20BJP's%20ideological%20parent%20RSS%2C%20and%20asked%20several%20questions%20on%20the%20BJP's%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20asked%20if%20the%20RSS%20supports%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Bwrongdoings%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20are%20openly%20distributing%20money%2C%20does%20RSS%20support%20buying%20votes%3F%20The%20names%20of%20Dalit%20and%20Purvanchali%20voters%20are%20being%20struck%20off%20(from%20voter%20lists)%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20Does%20RSS%20think%20this%20is%20good%20for%20democracy%3F%20Doesn't%20RSS%20feel%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20weakening%20democracy%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20is%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20embarrassing%20the%20BJP%20amid%20a%20bitter%20campaign%20for%20the%20capital%20contest.%20While%20AAP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20getting%20voters'%20names%20struck%20off%20the%20list%20in%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20win%20the%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20ruling%20party%20of%20getting%20fake%20voters'%20names%20added%20to%20the%20list%20to%20bolster%20its%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20responded%20sharply%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20letter%20with%20a%20letter.%20State%20BJP%20President%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20I%20have%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal...we%20hope%20that%20you%20will%20abandon%20your%20wrong%20habits%20of%20lying%20and%20deceit%20and%20bring%20meaningful%20change%20within%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20letter%20to%20the%20RSS%20chief%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20grab%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20attention%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20write%20to%20the%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20learn%20from%20it.%20Learn%20the%20spirit%20of%20service%2C%20leave%20behind%20your%20political%20moves%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Rajya%20MP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20neither%20vision%20nor%20candidates%20for%20the%20Delhi%20election.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20wants%20to%20win%20this%20election%20somehow%20by%20using%20dishonest%20means.%20But%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20won't%20let%20this%20happen.%20We%20won't%20let%20them%20win%20by%20using%20the%20tactics%20they%20are%20said%20to%20have%20used%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asking%20Delhiites%20to%20keep%20checking%20names%20on%20voter%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20launched%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency%20that%20he%20represents.%20%26quot%3BIn%2015%20days%2C%20they%20have%20put%20in%20applications%20to%20delete%20names%20of%205%2C000%20voters%20and%20also%20applied%20for%20the%20addition%20of%207%2C500%20names%20to%20the%20voter%20list.%20The%20total%20votes%20in%20my%20constituency%20is%201%20lakh%206%20thousand.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20holding%20an%20election%20then%3F%20A%20game%20is%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20name%20of%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20said%20a%20summary%20revision%20was%20carried%20out%20earlier%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20released%20a%20revised%20voter%20list%20on%20October%2029.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%2012%20per%20cent%20difference%20as%20the%20BJP%20claims%2C%20was%20the%20poll%20body's%20summary%20revision%20wrong%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20plans%20to%20get%20people%20from%20outside%20and%20register%20them%20as%20Delhi%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefuting%20the%20charges%2C%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20Virendraa%20Sachdeva%20said%20the%20number%20of%20voters%20in%20Delhi%20saw%20a%20huge%20jump%20between%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20the%20Assembly%20election%20next%20year.%20The%20same%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20observed%20after%20the%202019%20general%20election.%20%26quot%3BWho%20got%20these%20new%20voters%3F%20There%20are%20no%20answers.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20play%20the%20same%20game%20this%20time.%20BJP%20is%20saying%20those%20who%20don't%20live%20in%20Delhi%20anymore%2C%20those%20who%20have%20died%2C%20why%20should%20their%20names%20be%20on%20the%20list%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20alleged%20that%20fake%20documents%20were%20being%20used%20to%20get%20fake%20voters'%20names%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20also%20warned%20officers%20against%20committing%20irregularities%20at%20the%20BJP's%20behest.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20officers%2C%20you%20will%20be%20pressured%20to%20commit%20wrong%20acts%20but%20remember%2C%20you%20will%20sign%20the%20papers%20and%20these%20signatures%20will%20stay.%20Today%20or%20tomorrow%2C%20the%20government%20will%20change%2C%20but%20the%20files%20and%20signatures%20will%20stay.%20Work%20as%20per%20law%2C%20you%20will%20be%20in%20trouble.%20The%20ones%20who%20are%20giving%20the%20orders%20would%20escape.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20had%20written%20to%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20in%20September%20too%2C%20asking%20asking%20five%20questions%20related%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20leadership.%20The%20letter%20raised%20questions%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20actions%20and%20the%20NDA%20government's%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20central%20agencies%20to%20target%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735724220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fcdvr4vjo_arvind-kejriwal-mohan-bhagwat_625x300_01_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-mohan-bhagwat-does-rss-support-buying-votes-arvind-kejriwal-writes-to-mohan-bhagwat-7375557%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20campaign%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Election%2C%20party%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20BJP's%20ideological%20parent%20RSS%2C%20and%20asked%20several%20questions%20on%20the%20BJP's%20politics.