CCrush%20Hamas%E2%80%9D%20and%20release%20the%20hostages.%20The%20IDF%20carried%20out%20air%20strikes%20across%20Gaza%20for%20weeks%2C%20before%20launching%20a%20full-scale%20invasion%2C%20first%20in%20the%20north%2C%20and%20then%20expanding%20to%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20enclave.%20In%20the%20initial%20stage%2C%20more%20than%201%20million%20people%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20were%20ordered%20by%20the%20IDF%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20within%2024%20hours.%20Gaza%20City%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20the%20largest%20city%20in%20the%20enclave%2C%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20pile%20of%20rubble%20within%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fo24qgun8_original-sin_625x300_01_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Ccite%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20cover%20of%20Original%20Sin.%20Courtesy%3A%20HarperCollins%20India)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fcite%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20disproportionate%20force%20against%20the%20enemy%20is%20a%20well-known%20Israeli%20method%20(the%20Dahiya%20doctrine).%20Dahiya%20in%20Lebanon%20was%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Hezbollah%2C%20the%20Shia%20militia.%20In%20the%202006%20war%20with%20Hezbollah%2C%20Israel%20carried%20out%20widespread%20bombing%20of%20Dahiya%2C%20flattening%20the%20town.%20In%20October%202008%2C%20while%20warning%20Hezbollah%20amid%20tensions%20in%20northern%20Israel%2C%20General%20Gadi%20Eisenkot%2C%20then%20head%20of%20the%20Army's%20Northern%20Division%2C%20said%20Israel%20would%20use%20%E2%80%9Cdisproportionate%20force%E2%80%9D%20to%20destroy%20Lebanese%20villages%20from%20where%20Hezbollah%20was%20firing%20rockets.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20happened%20in%20the%20Dahiya%20quarter%20of%20Beirut%20in%202006%20will%20happen%20in%20every%20village%20from%20which%20Israel%20is%20fired%20on...%20From%20our%20standpoint%2C%20these%20are%20not%20civilian%20villages%2C%20they%20are%20military%20bases%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gen.%20Eisenkot%2C%20who%20later%20became%20Israel's%20Chief%20of%20General%20Staff%20and%20then%20a%20minister%20in%20Netanyahu's%20Cabinet.%20Post-7%20October%2C%20the%20IDF%20followed%20the%20same%20tactics%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202024%2C%20I%20met%20an%20Israeli%20journalist%2C%20who%20calls%20himself%20a%20right-winger%2C%20in%20Jerusalem.%20We%20had%20an%20open%20discussion%20about%20the%20war%20and%20Israel's%20objectives%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20Old%20City.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'This%20War%20Has%20A%20Cost'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20of%20the%20war%20were%20visible%20everywhere.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20Jerusalem%20the%20last%20time%2C%20the%20flea%20market%20near%20Jaffa%20Street%20was%20so%20crowded%20that%20I%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20walk%20in%20between%20traders%20and%20shoppers.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20a%20ghost%20street%2C%20with%20only%20a%20few%20shops%20being%20open.%20Restaurants%20were%20mostly%20empty.%20A%20tour%20guide%20I%20had%20met%20on%20my%20previous%20trip%20told%20me%20the%20war%20took%20a%20huge%20hit%20on%20the%20economy.%20At%20the%20Church%20of%20Holy%20Sepulchre%2C%20the%20fourth-century%20church%20that%20is%20considered%20the%20holiest%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20Christianity%2C%20there%20was%20hardly%20anyone%20besides%20our%20group%20when%20we%20visited%20the%20place%20in%20the%20evening.%20The%20journalist%20told%20me%20that%20like%20every%20war%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20one%20also%20has%20a%20cost.%20And%20Israelis%20are%20bearing%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%207%20October%20changed%20everything.%20Things%20can't%20just%20go%20back%20to%20the%207%20October%20status%20quo%2C%20he%20said.%20I%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20collective%20punishment%20of%20Gazans.%20The%20journalist%2C%20a%20kippah-wearing%2C%20bearded%20man%20in%20his%20early%20forties%2C%20said%20there%20was%20a%20debate%20on%20whether%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20were%20culpable%20in%20the%20whole%20disaster%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20what%20sense%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20voted%20for%20Hamas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20are%20you%20saying%20that%20they%20should%20be%20punished%20as%20a%20whole%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20that's%20not%20what%20I%20am%20saying.%20Hamas%20is%20part%20of%20Gaza's%20society.%20You%20look%20at%20their%20charter.%20They%20are%20committed%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20Israel.%20And%20they%20were%20still%20voted%20to%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20that%20case%20Likud's%20founding%20charter%20also%20lays%20claims%20to%20the%20land%20between%20the%20River%20and%20the%20Sea%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20Likud%20has%20been%20in%20power%20in%20Israel%20for%20how%20many%20years!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can't%20compare%20a%20legitimate%20ruling%20political%20party%20with%20a%20terrorist%20entity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20told%20me%20he%20didn't%20agree%20with%20the%20military%20tactics%20the%20IDF%20is%20using%20in%20Gaza.%20By%20that%20time%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20Gaza's%20population%20had%20been%20displaced.%20People%20in%20the%20north%20and%20central%20Gaza%20had%20been%20pushed%20to%20the%20Rafah%20border%20in%20the%20south.%20There%20was%20a%20growing%20international%20demand%20to%20let%20Gazans%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20north.%20%E2%80%9CEverybody%20says%20people%20in%20Gaza%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20return%20to%20Gaza%20City%20and%20Khan%20Younis.%20But%20where%20will%20they%20go%3F%20There%20is%20not%20a%20single%20building%20standing%20in%20northern%20Gaza.%20The%20whole%20city%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIsn't%20this%20mindless%20vengeance%3F%20Does%20this%20help%20Israel%20meet%20its%20long-term%20strategic%20objectives%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20know.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20if%20there's%20a%20strategy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20replied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'The%20War%20Will%20Be%20Long'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20at%20a%20Committee%20Room%20in%20the%20Knesset%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Parliament%2C%20I%20met%20Boaz%20Bismuth%2C%20a%20Member%20of%20the%20Knesset%20(MK)%20from%20Netanyahu's%20Likud%20Party.%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20saw%20an%20end%20to%20the%20war.%20Six%20months%20into%20the%20war%2C%20Israel%20had%20not%20met%20any%20of%20its%20declared%20objectives.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20war%20will%20be%20long.%20At%20least%20one%20year.%20We%20are%20making%20progress.%20We%20will%20meet%20our%20objectives%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBismuth%2C%20a%20bespectacled%2C%20clean-shaven%2C%20tall%20man%20with%20dark%20hair%2C%20wore%20a%20dark%20blue%20suit%20and%20tie.%20He%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20but%20was%20careful%20with%20the%20words%20he%20used.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20a%20journalist%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20probably%20recalling%20his%20stint%20as%20the%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EIsrael%20Hayom%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Hebrew%20language%20daily.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20joined%20Likud%20and%20became%20an%20MK.%20Ever%20since%20the%207%20October%20attack%20happened%2C%20Bismuth%20has%20taken%20a%20hardline%20position%20on%20the%20war%2C%20calling%20for%20erasing%20Hamas.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cruel%20and%20monstrous%20people%20from%20Gaza%20took%20an%20active%20part%20in%20the%20pogrom%20in%20the%20Israeli%20settlements%2C%20in%20the%20systematic%20murder%20of%20Jews%20and%20the%20shedding%20of%20their%20blood%2C%20in%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20children%2C%20old%20people%2C%20and%20mothers%2C%20and%20in%20tying%20up%20babies%20and%20burning%20them%20alive!%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20on%20October%2016.%20%E2%80%9COne%20mustn't%20pity%20the%20cruel%2C%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20any%20humanitarian%20gesture%E2%80%94the%20memory%20of%20Amalek%20must%20be%20erased!%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20biblical%20enemy%20nation%20of%20the%20Israelites.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20two%20objectives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bismuth%20told%20me%20in%20the%20Knesset%20committee%20room.%20%E2%80%9COne%20is%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20hostages.%20And%20the%20other%20is%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas.%E2%80%9D%20While%20asked%20about%20the%20mounting%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20Gaza%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20at%20war%20against%20civilians.%20I%20am%20at%20war%20against%20Hamas.%20People%20in%20Gaza%20elected%20Hamas.%20Still%2C%20I%20am%20not%20at%20war%20against%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Bismuth%2C%20sustainable%20peace%20is%20possible%20in%20the%20region%20only%20if%20Hamas%20is%20defeated.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20lose%20the%20war%2C%20we%20lose%20the%20idea%20of%20peace.%20If%20I%20lose%2C%20I%20lose%20everything.%20So%2C%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20lose%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20India%2C%20should%20support%20Israel%20in%20this%20war%20instead%20of%20attacking%20the%20way%20Israel%20is%20conducting%20the%20war.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20country%20that%20respects%20itself%20should%20call%20Hamas%20what%20it%20is%E2%80%94a%20terrorist%20entity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20Are%20Aware%20Of%20The%20Dangers'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20politician's%20view%20of%20the%20war.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20Israeli%20Foreign%20Ministry%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20where%2C%20inside%20a%20meeting%20room%2C%20I%20met%20Michel%20Ronen%2C%20a%20senior%20diplomat%20who%20headed%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Southeast%20Asia%20at%20the%20ministry.%20I%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20diplomatic%20fallout%20of%20the%20war.%20By%20that%20time%2C%20much%20of%20the%20global%20opinion%20had%20turned%20against%20Israel.%20There%20were%20cracks%20in%20Israel's%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%2C%20its%20biggest%20backer%2C%20which%20was%20becoming%20increasingly%20impatient%20with%20the%20mounting%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20working%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20political%20and%20international%20legitimacy%20stays%20for%20our%20military%20operations.%20We%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20dangers.%20We%20lost%20international%20support%20for%20our%20military%20operation%20in%201973.%20The%20UN%20demanded%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20three%20weeks.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20we%20see%20more%20flexibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ambassador%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20met%20him%2C%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%2C%20with%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20were%20already%20mediating%20ceasefire%20talks%20between%20Israel%20and%20Egypt.%20Cairo%20hosted%20the%20talks.%20I%20asked%20the%20ambassador%20about%20the%20military%20goals%20Israel%20had%20set%20and%20the%20role%20of%20diplomacy%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20ongoing%20war.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20looking%20at%20a%20victory%20formula.%20We%20want%20hostages%20back.%20That's%20what%20our%20urgent%20priority%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20will%20a%20hostage%20deal%20lead%20to%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%3F%20Hamas%2C%20which%20struck%20a%20limited%20deal%20with%20Israel%20in%20November%20and%20released%20some%20100%20hostages%20in%20return%20for%20a%20week-long%20ceasefire%2C%20later%20demanded%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%20for%20another%20hostage%20deal.%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20guarantee%20what%20would%20happen%20after%20a%20deal.%20There%20could%20be%20a%20ceasefire%20or%20there%20could%20be%20more%20attacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ambassador%20Ronen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20larger%20Palestine%20question.%20He%20gave%20the%20standard%20reply%3A%20Israel%20will%20continue%20working%20with%20its%20partners%20for%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmbassador%2C%20as%20a%20diplomat%2C%20do%20you%20still%20believe%20a%20two-state%20solution%20is%20possible%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20before%20wrapping%20up%20our%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20here%20call%20the%20two-state%20solution%20a%20two-state%20illusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20came%20his%20quick%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Disclaimer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20author%20and%20publisher%20of%20the%20book%20are%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20book%20or%20any%20excerpt%20derived%20therefrom.%20NDTV%20shall%20not%20be%20responsible%20or%20liable%20for%20any%20claims%20arising%20from%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20book%20including%20any%20claims%20of%20defamation%2C%20infringement%20of%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20or%20any%20other%20right%20of%20any%20third%20party%20or%20of%20law.%20Paragraph%20breaks%20and%20subheadings%20have%20been%20added%20by%20NDTV%20for%20readers'%20ease.%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735722540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F6ob8jm28_gaza-afp_625x300_26_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbook-excerpts%2Fisrael-palestine-war-two-state-solution-or-two-state-illusion-7376397%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3B'Isn't%20this%20mindless%20vengeance%3F%20Does%20this%20help%20Israel%20meet%20its%20long-term%20strategic%20objectives%3F'%20I%20asked%20the%20Israeli%20journalist.%20'I%20don't%20know.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20if%20there's%20a%20strategy%2C'%20he%20replied.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbook-excerpts%2Fisrael-palestine-war-two-state-solution-or-two-state-illusion-7376397%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%