%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-becomes-first-indian-airline-to-offer-wi-fi-on-domestic-flights-125010100470_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSaved%20Their%20Honour%26quot%3B%3A%20UP%20Man%20Kills%20Mother%2C%204%20Sisters.%20Records%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%2024-year-old%20man%20accused%20of%20murdering%20his%20mother%20and%20four%20sisters%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Lucknow%20has%20said%20in%20a%20chilling%20video%20that%20he%20committed%20the%20killings%20because%20he%20did%20not%20want%20his%20%26quot%3Bsisters%20to%20be%20sold%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20which%20emerged%20hours%20after%20the%20shocking%20crime%2C%20Arshad%20alleges%20that%20neighbours%20and%20land%20mafia%20in%20their%20hometown%20Budaun%20captured%20their%20house%20and%20planned%20to%20traffick%20his%20sisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Arshad%20said%20he%20killed%20his%20mother%20and%20three%20sisters%20and%20the%20fourth%20was%20about%20to%20die.%20He%20also%20showed%20the%20bodies%20and%20said%20he%20choked%20them%20and%20slit%20their%20wrists%20and%20that%20his%20father%20helped%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20his%20mother%20Asma%20and%20sisters%20Alia%20(9)%2C%20Alshia%20(19)%2C%20Aksa%20(16)%20and%20Rahmeen%20(18).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20family%20has%20taken%20this%20step%20due%20to%20harassment%20by%20people%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20I%20have%20killed%20my%20mother%20and%20sisters.%20When%20police%20get%20this%20video%2C%20they%20must%20know%20that%20the%20locals%20are%20responsible.%20They%20harassed%20us%20to%20capture%20our%20house.%20We%20raised%20our%20voice%2C%20but%20no%20one%20heard.%20It%20has%20been%2015%20days%20that%20we%20have%20been%20sleeping%20on%20the%20footpath%2C%20wandering%20in%20the%20cold.%20We%20don't%20want%20the%20children%20to%20wander%20in%20the%20cold.%20They%20have%20captured%20our%20house.%20The%20documents%20are%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Arshad%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20at%20the%20crime%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20young%20man%20said%20the%20family%20wanted%20to%20convert%20and%20appealed%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20named%20several%20people%20allegedly%20responsible%20for%20the%20deaths%3A%20Ranu%2C%20Aftab%2C%20Aleem%20Khan%2C%20Salim%2C%20Arif%2C%20Ahmad%20and%20Azhar.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20land%20mafia%2C%20they%20also%20sell%20girls.%20They%20planned%20to%20frame%20the%20two%20of%20us%20(him%20and%20his%20father)%20in%20a%20false%20case%20and%20sell%20our%20sisters.%20We%20did%20not%20want%20that.%20So%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20kill%20my%20sisters%20by%20choking%20them%20and%20slitting%20their%20wrists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20then%20showed%20the%20bodies%20of%20his%20mother%20and%20sisters.%20%26quot%3BI%20may%20not%20be%20alive%20till%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20suggesting%20that%20he%20had%20planned%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%20too.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20from%20Budaun%2C%20my%20aunt%20has%20proof%20(of%20residence)%20going%20back%20to%201947.%20They%20spread%20lies%20about%20us%20that%20we%20are%20Bangladeshis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20said%20in%20the%20video%20that%20the%20family%20wanted%20to%20convert%20to%20live%20in%20peace.%20%26quot%3BWe%20approached%20many%20people%20for%20help%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20help%20us.%20Now%20my%20sisters%20are%20dying%20and%20I%20will%20die%20in%20a%20short%20while.%20But%20no%20family%20in%20India%20should%20be%20forced%20to%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20requesting%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20justice.%20%26quot%3BI%20request%20with%20folded%20hands%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20justice%20in%20life%2C%20at%20least%20give%20us%20justice%20in%20death.%20They%20should%20get%20the%20strictest%20punishment.%20They%20are%20connected%20with%20leaders%20and%20police.%20They%20captured%20half%20of%20our%20plot%20and%20wanted%20to%20capture%20the%20other%20half.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20also%20said%20that%20a%20temple%20should%20come%20up%20on%20their%20land%20and%20their%20belongings%20must%20be%20donated%20to%20an%20orphanage%20so%20that%20our%20souls%20find%20joy.%20%26quot%3BI%20killed%20them%20with%20my%20father.%20What%20choice%20did%20I%20have%3F%20See%20them%20being%20sold%20in%20Hyderabad%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnsure%20they%20get%20justice.%20They%20struggled%20a%20lot%20today.%20We%20have%20saved%20their%20honour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20addressing%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20cannot%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Central%20Lucknow%2C%20Raveena%20Tyagi%20said%20the%20murders%20were%20committed%20at%20Hotel%20Sharanjit.%20%26quot%3BThe%20accused%2C%20identified%20as%20Arshad%20(24)%2C%20allegedly%20killed%20five%20members%20of%20his%20own%20family.%20Following%20the%20gruesome%20act%2C%20the%20local%20police%20promptly%20caught%20the%20accused%20from%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForensic%20teams%20have%20collected%20samples%20from%20the%20crime%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735721280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Flq69s9j_lucknow-murder-_625x300_01_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flucknow-five-murders-didnt-want-them-to-be-sold-up-mans-video-after-killing-mother-sisters-7376110%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2024-year-old%20man%20accused%20of%20murdering%20his%20mother%20and%20four%20sisters%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20Lucknow%20has%20said%20in%20a%20chilling%20video%20that%20he%20committed%20the%20killings%20because%20he%20did%20not%20wan