tek-ipo-opens-on-jan-7-key-details-for-investors-from-rhp-125010100423_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%20Whistleblower%20Suchir%20Balaji's%20Parents%20Say%20Autopsy%20Points%20To%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20Suchir%20Balaji%2C%20a%20former%20employee%20ChatGPT%20maker%20OpenAI%2C%20have%20alleged%20that%20his%20autopsy%20had%20shown%20signs%20of%20struggle%20such%20as%20a%20head%20injury.%20Twenty-six-year-old%20Balaji%2C%20who%20had%20flagged%20ethical%20concerns%20about%20OpenAI's%20functioning%20after%20he%20left%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20giant%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20San%20Francisco%20flat%20in%20November.%20Authorities%20have%20said%20he%20had%20died%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalaji's%20parents%20Balaji%20Ramamurthy%20and%20Purnima%20Rao%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20about%20their%20son's%20tragic%20death%20and%20their%20fight%20for%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20read%20the%20second%20autopsy%2C%20there%20are%20signs%20of%20struggle%20such%20as%20head%20injury%2C%20more%20details%20from%20the%20autopsy%20reveal%20it%20is%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20his%20last%20conversation%20with%20his%20son%2C%20Mr%20Ramamurthy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20returning%20from%20a%20birthday%20trip%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20where%20he%20went%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20he%20was%20happy.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20for%20CES%20(a%20tech%20show)%20in%20January.%20At%20the%20end%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20going%20for%20dinner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20California%2C%20Suchir%20Balaji%20worked%20with%20OpenAI%20for%20nearly%20four%20years%20as%20a%20researcher.%20He%20quit%20in%20August%2C%20protesting%20against%20the%20AI%20giant's%20business%20practices.%20Suchir%20alleged%20that%20OpenAI%20had%20violated%20US%20copyright%20law%20and%20voiced%20his%20concern%20in%20a%20report%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20titled%20'Former%20OpenAI%20Researcher%20Says%20the%20Company%20Broke%20Copyright%20Law'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%20said%20Suchir%20was%20among%20the%20top%2010%20in%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20industry.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20he%20quit%20OpenAI%20and%20leave%20the%20AI%20industry%2C%20he%20was%20planning%20to%20start%20something%20in%20neuroscience%20and%20machine%20learning.%20Our%20suspicion%20is%20was%20he%20threatened%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20did%20they%20suppress%20him%3F%20he%20didn't%20pick%20up%20another%20job%2C%20maybe%20they%20threatened%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fbaoa9ea_openai_625x300_01_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchir%2C%20his%20mother%20said%2C%20had%20consulted%20a%20copyright%20attorney%20and%20figured%20out%20he%20was%20not%20doing%20anything%20wrong%20and%20they%20were%20just%20suppressing%20him.%20That's%20what%20made%20him%20go%20for%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20interview%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Suchir%20had%20told%20her%20he%20was%20working%20on%20some%20research%20and%20would%20publish%20it%20when%20ready.%20%26quot%3BIn%20his%20publication%2C%20he%20explains%20with%20mathematical%20basis%20that%20the%20modulated%20answer%20is%20not%20exactly%20as%20per%20the%20information%20fed%20to%20ChatGPT.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%20said%20Suchir%20had%20told%20her%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bwork%20of%20artistes%20and%20journalists%20are%20stolen%20(by%20ChatGPT)%20and%20that's%20very%20unethical%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20concurred%20with%20him.%20He%20was%20not%20fighting%20against%20OpenAI%2C%20he%20was%20standing%20for%20humanity%2C%20he%20says%20in%20his%20article%20that%20he%20thought%20AI%20would%20be%20good%20for%20humanity%20but%20it%20is%20more%20harm.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchir's%20mother%20said%20she%20had%20advised%20him%20to%20build%20up%20support%20for%20his%20cause%20and%20he%20was%20working%20on%20that.%C2%A0The%2026-year-old's%20parents%20say%20they%20believe%20the%20information%20Suchir%20had%20might%20have%20led%20to%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20the%20AI%20industry.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20so%2C%20we%20know%20now%20it%20is%20a%20powerplay%2C%20we%20have%20the%20autopsy%20report%20and%20he%20didn't%20take%20his%20life.%20Who%20and%20why%20is%20something%20we%20need%20to%20explore%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Ramarao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20X%20boss%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20OpenAI%20co-founder%20Elon%20Musk%20voiced%20support%20for%20Suchir%20Balaji's%20parents.%20In%20an%20X%20post%20in%20which%20Ms%20Rao%20said%20her%20son's%20murder%20was%20being%20passed%20off%20as%20suicide%2C%20Musk%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20suicide.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Ramarao%20said%20it%20was%20a%20great%20support%20for%20them%2C%20but%20clarified%20that%20they%20had%20not%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemanding%20an%20FBI%20investigation%20into%20her%20son's%20death%2C%20Suchir's%20mother%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20must%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20and%20give%20justice%20to%20my%20son%2C%20a%20precious%20life%20has%20been%20lost%2C%20it's%20a%20loss%20to%20tech%20industry%2C%20he%20was%20incredibly%20smart.%20At%20OpenAI%2C%20his%20former%20boss%20says%20he%20tweaked%20the%20algorithm%20and%20found%20an%20easy%20way%20of%20doing%20things%20and%20that%20made%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20ChatGPT.%20OpenAI%20keeps%20saying%20we%20are%20supporting%20the%20parents%2C%20we%20wonder%20how.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchir's%20parents%20said%20they%20had%20also%20