%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-cafe-owner-dies-by-suicide-amid-divorce-business-dispute-with-wife-7375191%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Congress%20Needs%20To%20Go%20Back%20To%20The%20Drawing%20Board%20In%202025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ffs6jsh98_sonia-gandhi-rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_28_March_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20policy%20formulators%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20met%20in%20Belagavi%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20on%20December%2026%20and%20devised%20a%20plan%20for%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party.%20The%20leaders'%20collective%20assembly%20decided%20to%20launch%20a%20campaign%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution%20and%20strengthen%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20the%20venue%20was%20symbolic%2C%20commemorating%20the%20100th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20location%20where%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20assumed%20the%20presidency%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20at%20its%2039th%20session.%20The%20retracing%20of%20steps%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20rediscover%20the%20party's%20roots%20and%20draw%20inspiration%20in%20dealing%20with%20current%20challenges%20emanating%20from%20the%20governing%20coalition%20led%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3Cbr%3E%5CnBuilding%20on%20the%20momentum%20from%20their%20campaign%20during%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20leaders%20emphasised%20that%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20is%20facing%20a%20grave%20threat%20from%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20and%20its%20lead%20party%20is%20eroding%20the%20social%20welfare%20and%20inclusive%20principles%20enshrined%20in%20the%20document%20by%20its%20architect%2C%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%20in%20Parliament%20with%20renewed%20vigour%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20moving%20forward%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20retain%20the%20space%20it%20gained%20in%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20It%20has%20drawn%20up%20a%20list%20of%20issues%20on%20which%20it%20aims%20to%20build%20public%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20major%20thrust%20of%20highlighting%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Constitution%20and%20disrespect%20for%20Dr%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20issues%20identified%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20foreign%20affairs.%20These%20include%20caste%20census%2C%20opposition%20to%20the%20One-Nation-One-Election%20plan%20and%20amendments%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20rules%2C%20rekindling%20the%20debate%20to%20revisit%20the%20Temples%20of%20Worship%20Act%20of%201991%2C%20the%20denial%20of%20political%20space%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20dilution%20of%20financial%20support%20for%20MNREGA%2C%20inadequate%20MSP%20for%20farmers%2C%20the%20promotion%20of%20oligarchies%2C%20demands%20for%20clarity%20on%20relations%20with%20China%2C%20and%20recent%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20highlighted%20issues%20are%20certainly%20ones%20any%20opposition%20would%20take%20up%20to%20demand%20a%20cogent%20response%20from%20the%20government.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20inherent%20right%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20carry%20out%20campaigns%20and%20stage%20protests%20when%20the%20situation%20warrants.%20These%20elements%20are%20integral%20to%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%20whose%20adage%20states%20that%20it%20is%20the%20job%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20oppose%2C%20expose%2C%20and%2C%20if%20possible%2C%20depose%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20resolution%20at%20the%20conclusion%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20whether%20the%20setbacks%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20over%20the%20past%20two%20months%20were%20discussed%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee.%20For%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20honest%20introspection%20has%20been%20notably%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20has%20lost%20three%20consecutive%20general%20elections%20since%202014.%20It%20managed%20to%20salvage%20some%20prestige%20this%20summer%20by%20reaching%20the%2099%20mark%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20achievement%20restored%20the%20Congress's%20status%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20lower%20house.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20the%20party%20has%20lost%20several%20state%20assembly%20elections.%20Worse%20still%2C%20it%20lost%20in%20states%20where%20pre-poll%20surveys%20and%20projections%20had%20predicted%20a%20comeback.%20Haryana%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20party%2C%20especially%20the%20Congress%2C%20should%20analyse%2C%20clinically%20and%20dispassionately%2C%20why%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20not%20been%20convinced%20by%20the%20narrative%20it%20has%20been%20setting.%20For%20example%2C%20after%20the%20setback%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20elections%2C%20political%20analysts%20argued%20that%20focusing%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20caste%20census%20and%20threats%20to%20the%20Constitution%20did%20not%20gain%20traction%E2%80%94five%20months%20after%20they%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20party's%20success%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Congress%20political%20managers%20at%20various%20levels%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20reliability%20of%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%2C%20the%20accuracy%20of%20electoral%20rolls%2C%20and%20the%20reported%20increase%20in%20voter%20turnout%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20Each%20of%20these%20points%20has%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20party's%20resolution%20emphasises%20similar%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Reservation%20policy%2C%20along%20with%20the%20caste%20census.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20indication%20that%20the%20party%20has%20conducted%20empirical%20studies%20to%20assess%20whether%20these%20issues%20resonate%20with%20the%20most%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20after%20setbacks%20in%201996%2C%201998%2C%20and%202014%2C%20the%20Congress%20did%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20under%20A.K.%20Antony.%20One%20of%20the%20factors%20identified%20was%20that%20economic%20reforms%20had%20caused%20a%20distancing%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Congress.%20In%20the%20previous%20century%2C%20this%20led%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%2C%20while%20economic%20reforms%20were%20necessary%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20have%20a%20human%20face.%20While%20in%20opposition%2C%20the%20Congress%20continued%20the%20practice%20of%20serious%20introspective%20conclaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourse%20corrections%20followed%20when%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20assumed%20office%2C%20and%20the%20party%20recast%20welfare%20measures%20as%20rights-based%20schemes%2C%20such%20as%20MNREGA%20and%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act.%20The%20post-2014%20introspection%20concluded%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20perceived%20as%20favouring%20minorities.%20The%20perception%20persists%2C%20while%20policy%20prescriptions%20to%20counter%20it%20are%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen.%20The%20Congress%20needs%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735716660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ffs6jsh98_sonia-gandhi-rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_28_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-needs-to-go-back-to-the-drawing-board-in-2025-7375895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2