3A%22Atishi%20Says%20Lt%20Governor%20Ordered%20Demolition%20Of%20Hindu%20Temples%2C%20He%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20Tuesday%20alleged%20that%20an%20order%20was%20issued%20by%20a%20panel%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bdirections%20of%20Lt%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%26quot%3B%20for%20demolition%20of%20multiple%20Hindu%20and%20Buddhist%20religious%20structures%2C%20a%20charge%20refuted%20by%20the%20Governor's%20office%20as%20%26quot%3Bcheap%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lt%20Governor%20secretariat%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20neither%20are%20any%20temples%2C%20mosques%2C%20churches%20or%20any%20other%20place%20of%20worship%20being%20demolished%2C%20nor%20has%20any%20file%20in%20this%20regard%20was%20received%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Saxena%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20she%20was%20informed%20that%20the%20'Religious%20Committee'%2C%20in%20a%20meeting%20on%20November%2022%2C%20ordered%20for%20demolition%20of%20the%20religious%20structures%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20decided%20by%20the%20Religious%20Committee%20%26quot%3Bon%20your%20directions%2C%20and%20with%20your%20approval%26quot%3B%20to%20demolish%20multiple%20religious%20structures%20across%20Delhi%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20reply%2C%20the%20Lt%20Governor%20secretariat%20alleged%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20playing%20%26quot%3Bcheap%20politics%26quot%3B%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20her%20as%20well%20as%20her%20predecessor%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20%26quot%3Bfailures%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20at%20all%2C%20the%20Governor%20has%20issued%20strict%20instructions%20to%20the%20police%20to%20maintain%20extra%20vigil%20against%20forces%20who%20may%20indulge%20in%20deliberate%20vandalism%20for%20political%20benefits.%20His%20instructions%20are%20being%20strictly%20followed%2C%20as%20was%20witnessed%20d