%20to%20go%20in%20the%20series%2C%20the%20coach-captain%20duo%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20reportedly%20set%20to%20be%20grilled%20by%20the%20BCCI%20top%20management%20over%20the%20recent%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20topic%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20retirement%20from%20Tests%20remains%20hot%20for%20two%20reasons.%20Firstly%2C%20the%20opening%20batter%20hasn't%20produced%20the%20runs%20required%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20his%20place%20in%20the%20team.%20Secondly%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20his%20credentials%20as%20a%20skipper%2C%20pushing%20the%20BCCI%20selection%20committee%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20transition%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20pundits%20have%20been%20discussing%20Rohit's%20exit%20from%20the%20longest%20format%2C%20especially%20after%20he%20sacrificed%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20playing%20XI%20at%20MCG%20in%20order%20to%20make%20space%20for%20himself%20as%20an%20opener%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20was%20a%20selector%20now%2C%20it%20depends%20on%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20but%20if%20he%20doesn't%20make%20runs...%20I'd%20be%20saying%2C%20'Rohit%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20your%20service.%20You've%20been%20a%20great%20player%2C%20but%20we're%20going%20to%20bring%20in%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20as%20captain%20for%20the%20SCG%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Australian%20batting%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mark%20Waugh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F440-mark-waugh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMark%20Waugh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%2C%20addressing%20the%20press%20conference%20after%20India's%20defeat%20in%204th%20Test%2C%20didn't%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20over%20his%20position%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stand%20where%20I%20am%20standing%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20the%20MCG%20loss.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20to%20think%20about%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20past.%20Obviously%2C%20few%20results%20haven't%20gone%20our%20way.%20As%20a%20captain%2C%20yes%2C%20that%20is%20disappointing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20as%20a%20batter%20as%20well%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20do%20are%20not%20falling%20into%20place.%20But%2C%20mentally%2C%20it's%20disturbing%20without%20a%20doubt.%20If%20you%20have%20come%20here%2C%20you%20want%20to%20successfully%20do%20what%20you%20are%20supposed%20to.%20If%20those%20things%20don't%20fall%20in%20place%2C%20that's%20a%20big%20disappointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20Rohit%20has%20only%20managed%20just%20164%20runs%20across%20the%20last%2015%20innings%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20averaging%20less%20than%2011.%20Gill%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20had%20twice%20as%20good%20numbers%20at%20least.%20Still%2C%20had%20to%20warm%20the%20bench%20in%20Melbourne.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGautam%20Gambhir's%20Curious%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Gambhir%20replaced%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20India's%20head%20coach%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20shock%20results%20have%20unfolded.%20Be%20it%20the%20ODI%20series%20loss%20again