%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20arose%20when%20people%20requested%20collars%20for%20puppies.%20However%2C%20as%20Rimjhim%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CGiving%20collars%20to%20smaller%20animals%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20dangerous.%20Because%20after%20the%20photo%20op%20is%20done%2C%20what%20are%20the%20chances%20that%20somebody%20will%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20animal%20as%20it%20grows%20up%3F%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20only%20provide%20small%20collars%20to%20known%20NGOs%20and%20volunteers%20who%20we%20knew%20and%20trusted%2C%20who%20could%20monitor%20and%20update%20them%20as%20they%20grew.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20proudly%20wearing%20a%20reflective%20collar%20during%20a%20Pawsitivity%20collaring%20drive%2C%20helping%20keep%20street%20animals%20safe%20at%20night.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20220717-WA0007-1733989282-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-389010%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPawsitivity%20aims%20to%20provide%20affordable%2C%20QR-enabled%20reflective%20collars%20to%20animal%20caretakers%2C%20easing%20their%20financial%20burden%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Tank%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20Animal%20Welfare%20Officer%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20speaks%20out%20of%20her%20own%20experience%20of%20working%20in%20the%20field.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20that%20during%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20firecrackers%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20panic%20and%20disorientation%20in%20dogs.%20So%20these%20QR%20collars%20really%20help%20in%20reconnecting%20the%20lost%20animals%20to%20their%20caretakers%20or%20NGOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%E2%80%99s%20group%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%20relies%20heavily%20on%20these%20collars%2C%20as%20they%20are%20a%20lifesaver%20on%20highways.%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20them%2C%20many%20dogs%20would%20be%20invisible%20to%20drivers%2C%20and%20accidents%20are%20inevitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducating%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20the%20animal%20welfare%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETushar%20Shende%20(39)%2C%20Rimjhim%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20has%20been%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20Pawsitivity%20journey%2C%20handling%20the%20administrative%20and%20operational%20aspects%20of%20the%20venture%20along%20with%20his%20own%20job.%20Tushar%2C%20who%20was%20once%20terrified%20of%20dogs%2C%20now%20understands%20their%20needs%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20spreading%20awareness%20about%20responsible%20feeding%20and%20animal%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20both%20have%20been%20conducting%20school%20awareness%20programmes%20to%20teach%20children%20how%20to%20safely%20approach%20stray%20dogs%20and%20behave%20around%20them.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lack%20of%20understanding%20can%20lead%20to%20either%20the%20children%20hurting%20the%20animal%20or%20getting%20hurt%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20teach%20children%20how%20to%20safely%20and%20respectfully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F379789%2Fkind-hour-foundation-mouli-mehrotra-lucknow-art-education-animal-welfare-compassion-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteract%20with%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20creating%20positive%20experiences%20for%20both%20the%20animals%20and%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20programmes%20are%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20Pawsitivity%E2%80%99s%20mission%2C%20ensuring%20that%20children%20grow%20up%20with%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20street%20animals%20and%20a%20greater%20sense%20of%20empathy%20towards%20them.%20With%20Rimjhim%E2%80%99s%20connections%20as%20a%20former%20teacher%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20access%20various%20schools%20and%20run%20workshops%20that%20sensitise%20young%20minds%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20stray%20animals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rimjhim%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20faced%20many%20challenges%2C%20including%20financial%20difficulties%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20their%20passion%20for%20animal%20welfare%20has%20never%20faltered.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20pregnant%20during%20COVID%2C%20things%20were%20especially%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rimjhim%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20got%20a%20big%20order%20from%20an%20NGO%20that%20kept%20us%20going.%20It%20was%20during%20that%20time%20that%20I%20realised%20how%20much%20support%20we%20had%20from%20the%20animal%20welfare%20community.%20Our%20friend%20and%20supporter%2C%20the%20late%20Meenakshi%20Mahapatra%2C%20was%20truly%20an%20angel%20and%20helped%20us%20when%20we%20thought%20we%20would%20have%20to%20stop%20the%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawsitivity%20has%20seen%20significant%20growth%2C%20with%20revenue%20reaching%20Rs%2056%20lakh%20in%202023%20and%20projections%20for%202024%20set%20at%20Rs%2077%20lakh.%20The%20company%20has%20served%20over%201.5%20lakh%20customers%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F272456%2Fcat-cafe-studio-mumbai-lets-you-adopt-stray-animals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimal%20feeders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20pet%20owners%20looking%20to%20better%20the%20safety%20of%20stray%20dogs%20and%20other%20animals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERimjhim%E2%80%99s%20focus%20remains%20on%20providing%20affordable%2C%20high-quality%20reflective%20collars%20to%20these%20groups%2C%20while%20also%20empowering%20women%20and%20supporting%20broader%20animal%20welfare%20efforts.%20The%20company%E2%80%99s%20pricing%20structure%20has%20made%20the%20collars%20accessible%20to%20many%20feeders%20who%20would%20otherwise%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20afford%20such%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Rimjhim%20Joshi%20Shende%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735655400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-12-at-12.36.43-PM-1733988743.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D388977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20started%20as%20a%20simple%20desire%20to%20help%20street%20dogs%20has%20transformed%20into%20'Pawsitivity'%2C%20a%20successful%20business%20led%20by%20Rimjhim%2